  "prompt": "Where do I get all episodes of dragon ball Kai in English?",
  "response": "You can find all episodes of \"Dragon Ball Kai\" in English through various legal streaming platforms. Some options include:\n\n1. **Crunchyroll**: They often have a wide selection of anime, including \"Dragon Ball Kai,\" available for streaming with English subtitles and dubbed versions.\n\n2. **Funimation**: This service typically has the entire series available, with English dubbed episodes. A subscription may be required.\n\n3. **Hulu**: This platform may also have \"Dragon Ball Kai\" available for streaming, depending on your region.\n\n4. **Amazon Prime Video**: You can purchase episodes or entire seasons of \"Dragon Ball Kai\" through Amazon.\n\n5. **DVD/Blu-ray**: You can buy physical copies from retailers like Amazon, Best Buy, or Walmart.\n\nMake sure to check the availability based on your region, as streaming rights may vary.",
